title: Kubernetes: Component Status
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors the components of a kubernetes cluster.
 If a component is not healthy the check returns {CRIT} otherwise {OK}.
 If the status of a component is unknown the check returns {UNKNOWN}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each component.

item:
 The name of the component.
